1.0.0.name: wordpress/mh-magazine-lite
1.0.0.description: This is the free version of MH Magazine, a clean and modern magazine / blog WordPress theme for bloggers, online magazines, seo experts and other news or editorial related websites. If you would like to have more features and possibilities to customize your theme, you can purchase the premium version of MH Magazine on our website. To learn more about the theme, support options and to read the documentation, please open the file readme.txt which is included in the download package.
